Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:33.48,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,A preskoč bez uvažovania
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:36.32,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak neveríš na budúcnosť
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:38.46,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Pokračuj s tou silou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:40.63,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si sa ešte nenaučil
